Package src.user

Class Administrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.user.User
      • src.user.Administrator
  • public class Administrator
extends User
    Administrator class which extends User class. Administrator holds Company that is Administrator's company. Administrator has the abilities which are adding, removing, connecting branches etc..
